title: Colin Cowherd Podcast - Celtics/Warriors Game 5 Reaction
itunes:title: Colin Cowherd Podcast - Celtics/Warriors Game 5 Reaction
description:
Colin and Hoops Tonight  and Lakers Tonight Podcast host Jason Timpf react to the Warriors sitting on the verge of another title after taking a 3-2 Finals lead over the Celtics with a decisive Game 5 win at Oracle (3:00). They also look ahead to Game 6 and if the Dubs close it out in Boston, or if the Celts can force a Game 7 (24:00).

Follow Colin and The Volume on Twitter for the latest content and updates and check out FanDuel for the best wagering and daily fantasy action! #herd
